data.description: So much to appreciate in this conveniently located Hamilton Schools ranch. Open concept floor plan has a lovely flow & features a beautiful, central stone fireplace adding warmth & character to the entire living space. Hickory floors grace this area which includes a large living rm, dining rm, kitchen, & a huge walk-in pantry/mud rm. Updated kitchen w/snack bar has granite counters, appealing tile backsplash, & newer appliances. Large banks of windows provide ample natural light & views of the large trees on the private 0.69 acre lot. Main floor has 3 good size BRs w/wood floors under carpet per the Seller. Full and 1/2 baths have been updated. Lwr lvl has good potential, 2nd full bath & a small rec-room (currently used as BR) w/kitchenette. Make it yours & be in for the holidays!
